A man has landed himself in serious trouble after allegedly beating his daughter to death in Akure. A little girl has reportedly lost her life after being flogged mercilessly by her father. The tragic incident happened in Akure, Ondo state. According to Oluyemi Fasipe who shared the tragic news on Twitter, the little girl died after being rushed to the state hospital, Akure. He wrote: “I was just called that this child was allegedly beaten to death by the father. Unfortunately the corpse was taken away immediately from state hospital Akure children emergency room, I am going there now to make further enquires. This is so disheartening. “ Source